These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-1::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, comedy, fantasy, mystery
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, fanta, mirinda, hot-chocolate
There are 4 different nationalities: canadian, colombian, indonesian, polish
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, jet-ski, tram, trike
1. the colombian is the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
2. the indonesian is between the person watching fantasy movies and the person watching mystery movies##2
3. the colombian is the person driving the bus##1
4. the person driving the trike is on the left of the person driving the bus##1
5. the person drinking cola is on the left of the canadian##1
6. the person driving the tram is the person watching fantasy movies##1
7. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1
8. the canadian is on the far right##1
9. the person watching comedy movies is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy | mystery   | adventure  | fantasy  |
| Beverage   | fanta    | hot-chocolate    | cola      | mirinda    |
| Nationality   | polish | colombian | indonesian | canadian |
| Transport     | trike  | bus       | jet-ski    | tram     |

