.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-3::.
There 4 different types of food: artichoke, blueberry, lemon, mango
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, mirinda, iced-tea, fanta
The people have 4 different jobs:  analyst, lawyer, paramedic, pilot
The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, motorbike, roller, subway
1. the paramedic is the person driving the motorbike##1
2. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the pilot##1
3. the person driving the roller is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
4. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1
5. the person eating lemon is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
6. the lawyer is the person drinking fanta##1
7. the person eating mango is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
8. the person eating artichoke is between the person drinking 7up and the person drinking fanta##2
9. the person drinking iced-tea is between the person eating lemon and the lawyer##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2     |      3      |     4     |
| Food        | blueberry | lemon     | artichoke   | mango     |
| Beverage       | mirinda   | 7up   | iced-tea | fanta |
| Job         | analyst   | paramedic | pilot       | lawyer    |
| Transport   | roller    | motorbike | helicopter  | subway    |

