.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-5::.
There 4 different types of food: asparagus, garlic, lemon, peach
The people have 4 different jobs:  freelancer, lawyer, security-guard, social-worker
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, epic, romance, scientific
4 different pets are kept: pony, goat, guinea-pig, hamster
 1. the person eating lemon is on the right of the person eating garlic##1
 2. the owner of the pony is on the far left##1
 3. the security-guard is the person eating garlic##1
 4. the security-guard is on the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
 5. the person watching scientific movies is on the left of the person eating peach##1
 6. the person eating lemon is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1
 7. the social-worker is on the left of the person eating asparagus##1
 8. the lawyer is the person watching epic movies##1
 9. the person eating lemon is between the owner of the hamster and the person watching adventure movies##2
10. the person watching romance movies is the owner of the guinea-pig##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |       2       |       3       |     4      |
| Food          | garlic         | lemon         | asparagus     | peach      |
| Job           | security-guard | social-worker | freelancer    | lawyer     |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure      | romance       | scientific    | epic       |
| Pet         | pony     | guinea-pig       | hamster | goat |

