.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-7::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: family, fantasy, time-travel, zombie
City: miami, london, venice, hamburg
There are 4 different nationalities: argentine, british, dutch, russian
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, bike, subway, train
 1. the person driving the train is on the right of the person traveling to miami##1
 2. the person watching fantasy movies is the dutch##1
 3. the person traveling to london is between the dutch and the person driving the subway##2
 4. the person traveling to venice is the person driving the train##1
 5. the russian is on the left of the person watching zombie movies##1
 6. the person watching fantasy movies is on the left of the person driving the bike##1
 7. the argentine is the person driving the airplane##1
 8. the person traveling to hamburg is on the far right##1
 9. the person watching fantasy movies is on the right of the person watching time-travel movies##1
10. the dutch is the person driving the train##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel | fantasy | family  | zombie  |
| City   | miami       | venice   | london | hamburg    |
| Nationality   | argentine   | dutch   | russian | british |
| Transport     | airplane    | train   | bike    | subway  |

