.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-15::.
4 different games are played: domino, poker, backgammon, mah-jongg
There 4 different types of food: carrot, corn, pear, potato
4 different pets are kept: bird, ferret, horse, snake
The people use 4 different means of transport: boat, car, jet-ski, taxi
1. the person eating carrot is on the far right##1
2. the person driving the car is on the far left##1
3. the person playing poker is on the left of the person eating corn##1
4. the person playing domino is the person driving the taxi##1
5. the person playing domino is between the person driving the boat and the owner of the horse##2
6. the owner of the bird is on the left of the person playing backgammon##1
7. the person eating corn is the owner of the snake##1
8. the person playing mah-jongg is the person eating corn##1
9. the person playing poker is the person eating pear##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |   2   |   3    |    4    |
| Game    | poker | mah-jongg | domino  | backgammon |
| Food        | pear     | corn  | potato | carrot  |
| Pet         | ferret   | snake | bird   | horse   |
| Transport   | car      | boat  | taxi   | jet-ski |

